{
  "texts": [
    "The predictive inference can be available starting from the earliest phases of design -from the first sketch in terms of how a human drafts and develops a design.",
    "AI can go conveying the inference continuously in a way we can call whispering, providing the designerhuman as well as AI -with comprehensive feedback on his or its design decisions and heading of the design.",
    "This way, the design will be optimized not in the mode tryerror -correction -another error -another correction -and so forth till the designer is satisfied with the feedback parameters, or too tired to continue trying, which is the state-of-the-art today, but continuously.",
    "The effect in terms of time and cost spent, and quality of the solution achieved is obvious and huge; AI can never beat a human when it comes to true creativity -but no human intuition and experience combined compares to AI when it comes to parametric quantitative assessing and review.",
    "Here we go to the future of AECO."
  ]
}